what_worked: Applied prefetch_fact_join, single_pass_aggregation, materialize_cte: Restructured query with aggressive CTE chaining: created filtered CTEs for each dimension table to apply filters early, then joined them with the fact table in a single CTE before aggregation.
why_it_worked: Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1; Materializing a CTE used multiple times prevents redundant re-computation
